transmit(SeRequest) - Method in interface org.keyple.seproxy.ProxyReader
Transmits a request to a SE application and get back the corresponding SE response o the usage of this method is conditioned to the presence of a SE in the selected reader, this method could also fail in case of IO error or wrong card state → some reader’s exceptions (SE missing, IO error, wrong card state, timeout) have to be caught during the processing of the SE request transmission.
